<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Schedule is promulgated pursuant to Article 70 of the Telecommunications Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Dedicated Telecommunications Statutory Fees include the fees for examinations, inspection and license. The charge items and fee are as attached.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fees for examinations and inspection should be paid upon application; and the license free should be paid when it is issued.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[I. Applicant should pay the Statutory Fee in the form of cash, check issued by bank, treasury check, or draft to the NATIONAL COMMUNICATIONS COMMISSION.
II. The aforementioned check, treasury check or draft should be made payable to the NATIONAL COMMUNICATIONS COMMISSION.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Except for the case of over-payment, payment by mistake or by stipulation any other law provides, the payment shall not be returned after applicant pays the Statutory Fee according to the Schedule.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Schedule shall come into effect as of the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
